item.title: About me
item.description: This is a private blog website for the ETC5523 course arrangement. I will upload three blogs in this website. In the first blog, I will briefly introduce the Covid19 virus situation in Egypt. The theme was forked from @jrutheiser/hugo-lithium-theme and modified by Yihui Xie.
